blockedtext: Töi zangoguna ma alamat IP-mö no toba'agö. Same ba'a-ba'a $1. Börö $2. * Tebörögö mba'a-ba'a: $8 * Irugi: $6 * Niba'agö: $7 Sura khö 1 ma zui [[{{MediaWiki:Grouppage-sysop}}|administrator]] tanö bö'ö ba wamatunö womba'agö andre. Oguna'ö "{{int:emailuser}}" na no öbe alamat emailmö ba [[Special:Preferences|preferensi]] ba na lö niba'agö ndra'ugö wangoguna'ö email andrö. Alamat IP-mö $3, ba ID womba'agö #$5. Faogö fefu da'a yaŵa ero ösura wanofumö.
